OL,3,C'Death sentence': Woman whose dad died
OL,4,Cfrom pancreatic cancer calls for action
OL,6,FA woman from Newport whose dad and
OL,7,Funcle died from the most deadly common
OL,8,Fcancer, has joined calls for people
OL,9,Fwith pancreatic cancer to be fast-
OL,10,Ftracked onto clinical trials.
OL,12,FPancreatic cancer is the most fatal
OL,13,Fcommon cancer in the UK with half of
OL,14,Fpeople dying within three months of
OL,15,Fdiagnosis.
OL,17,FThe charity, Pancreatic Cancer UK,
OL,18,Fhave launched a campaign to fast-track
OL,19,Fpeople with the disease onto clinical
OL,20,Ftrials so better treatments can be
OL,21,Fdeveloped.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/7
