OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780506355
OL,3,C'Death sentence': Woman whose dad died
OL,4,Cfrom pancreatic cancer calls for action
OL,6,FPancreatic cancer is often diagnosed
OL,7,Fat a late stage, with people
OL,8,Fdeteriorating quickly. This makes it
OL,9,Fhard for eligible patients to be
OL,10,Fmatched up with trials as they often
OL,11,Fbecome too sick to take part.
OL,13,FPancreatic Cancer UK says these
OL,14,Fspecific difficulties are part of the
OL,15,Freason why there has been minimal
OL,16,Fimprovements in survival rates in the
OL,17,Flast 50 years.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/7
