PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780506355
OL,3,C'Death sentence': Woman whose dad died
OL,4,Cfrom pancreatic cancer calls for action
OL,6,FResearch by Pancreatic Cancer UK,
OL,7,Fbased on responses from over a
OL,8,Fthousand people with the disease,
OL,9,Frevealed that only 9% of patients had
OL,10,Fgenetic testing to to guide treatment
OL,11,For access to to clinical trials.
OL,13,FThe current situation means people are
OL,14,Fcommonly given life-extending
OL,15,Fchemotherapy, but patients are often
OL,16,Ftoo unwell to tolerate it. Seven in
OL,17,Ften people with the disease receive no
OL,18,Ftreatment at all.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/7
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
