PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1780506355
OL,3,C'Death sentence': Woman whose dad died
OL,4,Cfrom pancreatic cancer calls for action
OL,6,FIn response the Welsh Government in a
OL,7,Fstatement said: "This new government's
OL,8,FCancer Plan for Wales will outline the
OL,9,Fapproach toward research, innovation
OL,10,Fand improving access to clinical
OL,11,Ftrials so patients can benefit from
OL,12,Fnew treatments, including for
OL,13,Fpancreatic cancer."
OL,15,F"We are also planning a Wales Cancer
OL,16,FConference next year to bring together
OL,17,Fexperts and share best practice in
OL,18,Fcancer care."
OL,26,@oD@QOUuD@SO]wD@AOUzD@MO]
